vibesExplanation:
The workout 'Welcome to Norway Row' primarily embodies 'The Adrenaline Rush' vibe due to the HIIT format with 1-minute intervals and a maximum rhythm of 34, indicating high intensity and unpredictability, scoring a 0.7. Additionally, with a workout intensity level of 3 out of 3 and an advanced fitness level requirement, it fosters a full-body, heart-racing experience.

The 'Endorphin Wave' vibe is also present, scoring a 0.6, because of the elevated energy and feel-good components provided by a playlist featuring upbeat pop music ('Higher Love', 'Take On Me'), promoting a steady energy build throughout this brief but intense session.

Finally, 'The Explorer's Workout' vibe, scoring a 0.7, is supported by the scenic location in Nordåsvannet Bay, enhancing the adventurous, open-air experience and making the workout feel like an immersive exploration of Norway.
